Pastor Confidence Monyela (32) from Mariveni village near Nkowankowa outside Tzaneen, appeared at the Lenyenye Magistrate Court today on five charges of rapes, and one charge of sexual assault.Monyela was remanded in custody without bail until the 08 September 2017 for Social Worker&#8217;s report and for further Police investigations.Prophet Monyela of Prophet Ministry Church in Burgersdorp is alleged to have raped a 12-year-old girl, two 14 year-olds and a 16-year-old. It is alleged the pastor raped the victims on on various occasions. Reports suggests Monyela would invite them one by one to come to the church for prayer and while busy praying , he will then attack the victim and rape her.